All Implemented Interfaces:
javax.faces.component.ActionSource, javax.faces.component.NamingContainer, javax.faces.component.StateHolder
public class MenuItems
extends MenuItemBase

MenuItems is the JSF component class that represents a heirarchy of ICEfaces MenuItems.

This is the submenu component to use if you want to supply a (potentially) dynamic heirarchy of menuItems.

MenuItems extends the ICEfaces MenuItemBase component.

By default this component is rendered by the "com.icesoft.faces.View" renderer type.

1.1
